quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  24,32,"Ndesinee …ďe ndesaani …ďeen e moo…óon e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen immorde e muccu…ďe moo…óon e hor…ďe moo…óon, si …ďe laatike waas…ďe Alla al…óinat …ďe immorde e ∆Āural makko ngal, Alla ko o jaac…óo ganndu…óo."
  24,33,"∆Āe ke…ďaani fehre desugol …ďeen yo …ďe cabbo haa Alla al…óinira …ďe ∆Āural makko ngal. ∆Āeen …óa…ď…ďat…ďe soottaade e …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon njeyi, coottaadede …ďe si on nganndii e ma…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īere, njonnee …ďe immorde e jawdi Alla ndin, ndin ndi O jonni on, wota on waawnu hor…ďe moo…óon …ďen e fii jeeno, si …ďe faandike saŇčaade, wota on …óa…ď…ďu jawkal ngurndam aduna, kala waawnuu…óo …ďe pellet, Alla …ďaawo baawnugol …ďe ko O cuhroowo jurmitee…óo."
  24,34,"GooŇč…óii min njippinii e moo…óon aayeeje …ďanngu…óe e misal immorde e …ďeya wulinoo…ďe ko adii on e waaju wonan'de huloo…ďe [Alla] …ďen."
  24,35,"Ko Alla woni annoore kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, sifa annoore makko nde ko wano tu…ó…óere hara no e mayre pitilol(lampu), pitilol ngol wona e ndeer biiniiri, biiniiri ndin hara hindi wa'i wa hoodere jalbunde hinde hu…ď…ďa immorde e leggal barkinaangal nebbantewal ngal wonaa funnaangeyaŇčkowal ngal wonaa hirnaangeyaŇčkowal nebbam maggal …óam no …ďadoo jalbude, hay si yiite memaani …óam, annoore e hoore annoore, Alla no feewnira annoore makko nde oon mo o muuyi, Alla no piyana yim…ďe …ďen mise, Alla ko o ganndu…óo kala hu'unde."
  24,36,"E nder cuu…ói …ói Alla duŇčii(sakkiti) yo darne Innde makko jaŇčtee e ndeer majji Subunhinanee mo ndeer majji ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe."